quote: The trees reach up above me toward the sky, stretching out their great limbs in an intricate pattern that reminds me of the pattern of light... the pattern shifting back and forth as I climb.
quote_letters: THE TREES REACH UP ABOVE ME TOWARD THE SKY STRETCHING OUT THEIR GREAT LIMBS IN AN INTRICATE PATTERN THAT REMINDS ME OF THE PATTERN OF LIGHT THE PATTERN SHIFTING BACK AND FORTH AS I CLIMB
